data.description: *This Home Is Eligible For Up To $3k Down Payment Assistance- As Your Agent* Discover this charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath, 2-story home situated in South Bend's south side. This residence underwent a comprehensive remodel approximately one year ago, presenting a refreshed interior. The main level offers a spacious living room with a recently painted fireplace, a formal dining area, and an updated kitchen featuring newer cabinets, countertops, and modern appliances. Upstairs houses two ample bedrooms and a fully renovated bathroom. Throughout the interior, you'll find newer flooring, and upgraded fixtures. Additional perks include a one-year-old roof, updated windows, a recently painted exterior, and a brand-new front door. In the large basement you’ll find the washer and dryer which were purchased in 2023. Schedule your showing today!
